#week-title("Three", "The 22 Paths & The Major Arcana")

=== Core Teaching

The 22 paths between the sephiroth correspond to the 22 Major Arcana. Each Trump
traces a stage of the Great Work in symbolic sequence:

- *The Fool (0):* The beginning; undifferentiated prima materia.
- *Death (13):* Putrefaction; the Nigredo; transformation.
- *Temperance (14):* Distillation; the angelic operation of tempering opposites.
- *The World (21):* The completed Magnum Opus; the Stone manifested.

Understanding the paths allows the alchemist to map the movement of force between
different stages of consciousness and manifestation.

=== Topics This Week

- The 22 Paths as connections between sephiroth
- The Major Arcana as the alchemical stages in sequence
- Letter, Number, and Image encoding the Work

